OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry and mostly cloudy evening with
OL,7,Fsome late sunny intervals in the
OL,8,Fsouth. Remaining dry and mostly cloudy
OL,9,Fovernight. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA dry day and mostly cloudy
OL,12,Fin the north and west but the south
OL,13,Fand east seeing some good sunny spells
OL,14,Fbreaking through. Warm in the sunshine.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FMostly dry on Thursday with sunny
OL,18,Fspells. Then becoming mostly cloudy on
OL,19,FFriday with a little light rain
OL,20,Fpossible. Cloudy with rain, perhaps
OL,21,Fheavy, spreading eastwards on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
